Author: livipup
Text: Could be a release of seratonin coupled with lightheadedness

Author: iceicemilkshake
Text: Purging feels productive to me, and I’m super anxious about always staying on top of my to-do list. So being able to ‘complete’ something that is helping with weight loss or ‘fixing’ a binge, let’s feel like I’ve put in some work and deserve a break, so to speak.
